title: Håkan Stenbäck
text: Jan Sven Håkan Stenbäck (28 October 1951) is a Swedish former <a href="association%20football">football</a> player and manager. A <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a>, he made 199 <a href="Allsvenskan">Allsvenskan</a> appearances for <a href="Djurg%C3%A5rdens%20IF%20Fotboll">Djurgårdens IF</a> and scored 46 goals. He also played for <a href="Sandvikens%20IF">Sandvikens IF</a>.
